creator: Subsplash Inc
descriptionHtml: Kessid Church is a non-denominational Christian church located in Vancouver, WA. We are a community that believes we are better together than we are apart. The word “Kessid” means the attribute of grace, steadfast love, or mercy. Through Scripture and Spirit, we hope you will feel God’s love, experience community connection, build lasting friendships, and live out God’s calling for your life. For more information visit our website at kessid.com, or contact us at info@kessidchurch.com.

- Misc. bug fixes and improvements.
